<h1>International Weights and Measures Plugin For Rails</h1>

<p>
  This plugin allows you to use weight and measures in the same weight that one uses dates and times in rails.
</p>

Standard Syntax

<code>n = 1.kg + 1.kg</code>
<code>puts n </code> => <i>2.0 kg</i>
<code>n += 1.mg</code>
<code>puts n.to_s(:long)</code> => <i>2.000001 kilograms</i>
<code>n *= 4</code>
<code>puts n</code> => <i>8.000004 kg</i>
<code>n /= 2</code>
<code>puts n.to_s(:long)</code> => <i>4.000002 kilograms</i>
<code>n -= 1.hg</code>
<code>puts n</code> => <i>-0.099995999998 kg</i>

